<h1 style="text-align: center;">Who Are Our Volunteers?</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">Read here to meet our student volunteers, and learn about their roles!</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">There are a myriad of ways to be volunteer&nbsp;in Risley Hall! You can be a hall council officer, facilitate&nbsp;a major program, welcome as an&nbsp;Risley Orientation leader, educate as a Shop Manager, and more! All volunteer positions are about two hours a week, and count as campus service hours for the Cornell Tradition.</p>

