<h1 style="text-align: center;">Risley Orientation Leaders</h1>

<p style="text-align: center;">In addition to the <a href="https://ccengagement.cornell.edu/new-student-programs/orientation/volunteer-orientation">orientation leaders</a> trained by the New Student Programs Department, Risley Hall also has additional volunteers to help you between move in and the start of classes! Our two Ris-Lords lead and create Risley-specific programming, and our Ris-OC&#39;s help you move in and are available for any questions you might have! Risley Orientation Leaders&#39; appointments are until early September, and while you are welcome to always ask them questions, you are also encouraged to work with your RA&#39;s, who are available year-round!</p>

